®

, AND OTHER DATA SERVICES ARE CONSIDERED

DEREGULATED AND HAVE TOTAL PRICING FLEXIBILITY.

INDIANA

VERIZON NORTHS TELEPHONE OPERATIONS IN INDIANA ARE SUBJECT TO RATE OF RETURN

