REGULATES VERIZON VIRGINIAS NONCOMPETITIVE SERVICES ON A PRICE CAP BASIS AND

DOES NOT REGULATE VERIZON VIRGINIAS COMPETITIVE SERVICES. THE PLAN DOES NOT

